 Hybrid Automation Framework
 (Java, Selenium, TestNG, Maven, Page Object Model)

 1. Create Maven project
 (Add following dependencies on POM file.)
  - Selenium java
  - Apache poi
  - Poi xml
  - Log4j-core
  - log4j-api
  - commons-io
  - commons-lang3
  - testng
  - extent reports

  2. Folder structure
  projectABC
  src/test/java
    -pageObjects
    -testBase
    -testCases
    -utilities
  Src/test/resources
  JRE System Library
  logs
  reports
